text: DXWM (91.9 MHz) Radyo Rapido is an FM station owned and operated by Kalayaan Broadcasting System, Inc.. The studio is located in Capitol Hills, Mati City. It used to be known as Sunrise FM from 2008 to 2015, when it transferred to 102.5 to give way for the launching of Radyo Rapido. ==References== Category:Radio stations established in 2008
title: DXWM
